<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 14:07:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙边境附近被毁的以色列海滩将自战争开始以来首次开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/destroyed-israeli-beach-near-gaza-border-set-to-open-for-first-time-since-war-began/00000190-976d-d8d3-adb9-dfff48100000</link><description>10 月 7 日，加沙地带北部的齐金海滩 (Zikim beach) 发生了以色列国防军与哈马斯恐怖分子之间的激烈战斗，造成 11 名平民和 1 名士兵死亡。它已焕然一新，将于八月重新向公众开放</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 13:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/destroyed-israeli-beach-near-gaza-border-set-to-open-for-first-time-since-war-began/00000190-976d-d8d3-adb9-dfff48100000</guid></item><item><title>“我和许多其他预备役军人并没有参军执行浩劫”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-and-many-other-reservists-did-not-enlist-to-carry-out-a-nakba/00000190-916b-d0cb-abb9-f77b0e570000</link><description>八个月来，前以色列国防军国际媒体发言人彼得·勒纳（Peter Lerner）从一个工作室到另一个工作室，试图让全世界相信以色列国防军在加沙行动的合法性。现在他说：“在国际舞台上，内塔尼亚胡和他的政府带领以色列失败了”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 12:14:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-and-many-other-reservists-did-not-enlist-to-carry-out-a-nakba/00000190-916b-d0cb-abb9-f77b0e570000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构首次向以色列法院提交请愿书，希望推翻恐怖受害者赔偿法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/in-first-ever-petition-to-israeli-court-pa-looks-to-reverse-terror-victim-damages-laws/00000190-96ef-d8d3-adb9-deff2a800000</link><description>议会三月份颁布的法律允许恐怖袭击受害者及其家人向巴勒斯坦权力机构提起损害赔偿诉讼，但请愿书声称这些法律“违宪”，并将导致巴勒斯坦权力机构“经济崩溃”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:53:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/in-first-ever-petition-to-israeli-court-pa-looks-to-reverse-terror-victim-damages-laws/00000190-96ef-d8d3-adb9-deff2a800000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯10月7日袭击以色列7名加沙人，他们的命运不明</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-attacked-7-gazans-in-israel-on-october-7-their-fates-are-unknown/00000190-9684-dae0-a59d-96bc94d60000</link><description>在一张照片中，10 月 7 日遭到袭击的货车内有尸体。在另一张照片中，哈马斯恐怖分子从车里活捉了两人。除了尸体被送还给家人的司机外，九个月以来，以色列没有人知道其他加沙乘客的遭遇，直到上周</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-attacked-7-gazans-in-israel-on-october-7-their-fates-are-unknown/00000190-9684-dae0-a59d-96bc94d60000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人头部被海绵头子弹击中，以色列赔偿10万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-pay-100k-in-damages-to-palestinian-shot-in-the-head-with-sponge-tipped-bullet/00000190-96b1-d1c5-a1d6-befd39260000</link><description>六年前，这名东耶路撒冷居民因海绵头子弹近距离射击而造成神经损伤，随后起诉该州。调查该事件的机构结案后达成和解，该男子的律师指控其妨碍司法公正</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:35:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-pay-100k-in-damages-to-palestinian-shot-in-the-head-with-sponge-tipped-bullet/00000190-96b1-d1c5-a1d6-befd39260000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸定居点关闭通往巴勒斯坦城镇的道路，激怒安全官员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-settlement-closes-access-road-to-palestinian-town-angering-security-officials/00000190-968f-d1c5-a1d6-becfa1930000</link><description>阿里尔市市长封锁了道路，声称他正在帮助定居者的安全，但安全部门消息人士建议市长“让军队和国防机构负责创造安全”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-settlement-closes-access-road-to-palestinian-town-angering-security-officials/00000190-968f-d1c5-a1d6-becfa1930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队预计将起诉虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的预备役军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-expected-to-indict-reservist-over-treatment-of-palestinian-detainees/00000190-964f-d1c5-a1d6-becf11900000</link><description>一名士兵据称殴打戴着手铐的巴勒斯坦被拘留者，以色列军法署预计将提出虐待指控。据巴勒斯坦报道，最近几天在凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点附近发现了四名被拘留者，他们已经死亡并被戴上手铐。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:17:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-expected-to-indict-reservist-over-treatment-of-palestinian-detainees/00000190-964f-d1c5-a1d6-becf11900000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉最高法院，必须尽一切努力将囚犯从斯德泰曼拘留中心清除</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tells-top-court-all-efforts-must-be-made-to-clear-prisoners-out-of-sde-teiman/00000190-9677-d1c5-a1d6-beff09b60000</link><description>据国家检察官办公室称，目前该设施内关押着 166 名被拘留者。该国宣布打算在六月之前将他们转移到以色列的其他监狱或将他们送回加沙，但此后一再要求推迟</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 08:56:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tells-top-court-all-efforts-must-be-made-to-clear-prisoners-out-of-sde-teiman/00000190-9677-d1c5-a1d6-beff09b60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对加沙休战发表评论后，美国和卡塔尔等待以色列的澄清</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-qatar-waiting-for-israeli-clarifications-after-netanyahu-comments-on-gaza-talks/00000190-951b-d8d3-adb9-dddf39d40000</link><description>外国外交官表示，周三在卡塔尔与摩萨德主席大卫·巴尼亚的会晤将“至关重要”，因为调解人正在等待听取以色列是否根据内塔尼亚胡的“红线”文件提出任何弥合与哈马斯分歧的实际建议</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 03:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-qatar-waiting-for-israeli-clarifications-after-netanyahu-comments-on-gaza-talks/00000190-951b-d8d3-adb9-dddf39d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列购买芬兰反无人机系统以保护内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-purchased-foreign-anti-drone-system-to-protect-prime-minister-netanyahu/00000190-9279-dfc0-a3f3-bef911130000</link><description>在评估了以色列和外国的多种不同选择后，Shin Bet 购买了 Airfence 系统</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 03:00:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-purchased-foreign-anti-drone-system-to-protect-prime-minister-netanyahu/00000190-9279-dfc0-a3f3-bef911130000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列在贝鲁特-大马士革高速公路上袭击汽车；真主党播放以色列国防军基地的无人机镜头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-live/israeli-jets-hit-iranian-linked-targets-in-northern-syria-reports-claim/00000190-9542-d1c5-a1d6-bdce094c0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们拦截了两架从黎巴嫩越境进入以色列的无人机。 ■ 叙利亚军队报告称，以色列袭击了叙利亚北部与伊朗有关的目标，没有人员伤亡。 ■ 哈马斯称内塔尼亚胡为停火谈判设置了障碍；敦促调解人介入 ■辛贝特首席和以色列谈判团队在开罗进行交易谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 02:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-live/israeli-jets-hit-iranian-linked-targets-in-northern-syria-reports-claim/00000190-9542-d1c5-a1d6-bdce094c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列西岸高级官员在退休演讲中揭露了隐藏的真相</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/in-his-retirement-speech-israels-top-officer-in-the-west-bank-revealed-the-hidden-truth/00000190-93fc-d1c5-a1d6-bbfc58e20000</link><description>耶胡达·福克斯少将强调了忽视定居者针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力的危险以及巴勒斯坦权力机构对以色列安全的重要性</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 22:28:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/in-his-retirement-speech-israels-top-officer-in-the-west-bank-revealed-the-hidden-truth/00000190-93fc-d1c5-a1d6-bbfc58e20000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸以色列军事指挥官谴责定居者领导的针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-commander-in-west-bank-slams-settler-leadership-over-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-93fa-d8d3-adb9-dbfeb7490000</link><description>在指挥权变更仪式上，耶胡达·福克斯少将表示，“极端民族主义犯罪活动在战争的掩护下抬头”，并指责定居点运动的领导人没有采取任何行动来阻止它</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 22:17:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-commander-in-west-bank-slams-settler-leadership-over-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-93fa-d8d3-adb9-dbfeb7490000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔拒绝支持该法案，直到获得内塔尼亚胡安全席位为止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-refuses-to-support-bill-until-given-a-seat-at-netanyahus-security-table/00000190-93dd-d463-abda-ffddef8e0000</link><description>国家安全部长本-格维尔拒绝支持沙斯法案，直到总理将他纳入对战争做出关键决定的“小内阁”</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 20:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-refuses-to-support-bill-until-given-a-seat-at-netanyahus-security-table/00000190-93dd-d463-abda-ffddef8e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导层表示，内塔尼亚胡发表声明后，人质交易的可能性很小</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leadership-says-chances-slim-for-hostage-deal-following-netanyahus-statement/00000190-931d-dfc0-a3f3-bffdcd660000</link><description>加沙以外的哈马斯领导人指出，以色列总理的“原则清单”证明协议几乎没有机会。 加沙的一名官员告诉《国土报》，“内塔尼亚胡支持没有最后期限的谈判，以便赢得时间”，并且“任何人都希望取得突破”生活在幻觉中’</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:57:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leadership-says-chances-slim-for-hostage-deal-following-netanyahus-statement/00000190-931d-dfc0-a3f3-bffdcd660000</guid></item><item><title>以色列派往欧洲反犹太主义极右翼的流氓特使的奇案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-curious-case-of-israels-rogue-envoy-to-europes-antisemitic-far-right/00000190-92f5-dcf1-afdd-d2f5f2d40000</link><description>许多以色列人感到自己被政府背叛，因为政府未能在 10 月 7 日之前、期间和之后确保他们的安全。散居海外的犹太人现在知道他们的感受。以色列部长背叛了个人和社区的安全</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-curious-case-of-israels-rogue-envoy-to-europes-antisemitic-far-right/00000190-92f5-dcf1-afdd-d2f5f2d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 276 天：消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡在谈判代表中划定的休战“红线”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-276-netanyahus-red-lines-for-truce-box-in-negotiators-sources-say/00000190-933e-d1c5-a1d6-bbfe237e0000</link><description>以辛贝特为首的以色列代表团抵达开罗，继续人质释放谈判 ■ 以色列国防军将很快公布其对 10 月 7 日事件的调查结果。 美国 ■ 拜登表示，他对以色列和加沙的计划“非常接近”被执行 ■ 哈马斯高级官员据报道，加沙官员向该组织的政治梯队施压，要求他们接受拜登的停火提议，尽管辛瓦尔表示反对。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-276-netanyahus-red-lines-for-truce-box-in-negotiators-sources-say/00000190-933e-d1c5-a1d6-bbfe237e0000</guid></item><item><title>救赎之路|以色列对哈马斯的战争如何成为加沙犹太人定居点的跳板</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-08/ty-article-static/.premium/israel-seized-26-of-gaza-now-jewish-settlers-see-their-chance/00000190-77cd-d705-a7f5-fffffcbc0000</link><description>以色列国防军已经控制了加沙地带26%的地区，修建基地、铺设道路。以色列的宗教权利已经在朝着其目标前进。这就是以色列士兵眼中的样子</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:57:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-08/ty-article-static/.premium/israel-seized-26-of-gaza-now-jewish-settlers-see-their-chance/00000190-77cd-d705-a7f5-fffffcbc0000</guid></item><item><title>2024年上半年赴以色列旅游人数大幅下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/number-of-tourists-travelling-to-israel-drops-significantly-in-first-half-of-2024/00000190-92be-dcf1-afdd-d2fe0a9a0000</link><description>加沙战争期间，前往以色列的旅游人数下降了 76%，而以色列人仍然渴望出国航班 以色列统计机构报告</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:19:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/number-of-tourists-travelling-to-israel-drops-significantly-in-first-half-of-2024/00000190-92be-dcf1-afdd-d2fe0a9a0000</guid></item><item><title>斯塔默和马克龙本周无法给拜登的一条关键建议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-one-critical-piece-of-advice-starmer-and-macron-cant-give-biden-this-week/00000190-9293-dfc0-a3f3-bef388390000</link><description>政治命运截然不同、选举环境截然不同的三个亲密盟友将于本周在华盛顿举行的北约会议上会面。联盟的未来取决于对美国总统的政治建议，而英法领导人却无法真正提供这些建议</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:42:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-08/ty-article/.premium/the-one-critical-piece-of-advice-starmer-and-macron-cant-give-biden-this-week/00000190-9293-dfc0-a3f3-bef388390000</guid></item></channel></rss>